The paper proposes a method for reasoning in the description logic SHIQbs, which is commonly used in artificial intelligence and knowledge representation. The use of decision diagrams and disjunctive Datalog suggests a focus on logic and databases, which are covered by the cs.LO and cs.DB sub-categories. The paper also discusses knowledge compilation and complexity, which are relevant to the cs.AI and cs.SE sub-categories. Finally, the use of description logics and DL-safe rules points towards the cs.DL sub-category.
